text: The Enforcer is a 1976 American action thriller movie directed by first time director James Fargo and is the third movie in the Dirty Harry series. It stars Clint Eastwood, Tyne Daly, Harry Guardino, Bradford Dillman, John Mitchum, DeVeren Bookwalter, Albert Popwell, Robert Hoy and was distributed by Warner Bros.. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1976 action movies Category:1976 thriller movies Category:1970s American action movies Category:American thriller movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by James Fargo
